data.description: Welcome to 635 Cedar Ridge Drive, Neosho! This edge of town home features 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a finished walk-out basement. Nestled on 1.3 acres, this property provides both spacious living and a picturesque setting. Discover the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility in every room. Entertain guests in the expansive living areas, or retreat to the outdoor haven- a sprawling yard surrounded by nature. Come see this home for yourself before it's gone!
